all those things after this test, right?

00:01:10.818 --> 00:01:12.436
Well, not so fast.

00:01:12.436 --> 00:01:15.473
It turns out that sleep 
is also crucial for your brain,

00:01:15.473 --> 00:01:18.173
with a fifth of your body's 
circulatory blood

00:01:18.173 --> 00:01:20.853
being channeled to it as you drift off.

00:01:20.853 --> 00:01:23.460
And what goes on 
in your brain while you sleep

00:01:23.460 --> 00:01:26.541
is an intensely active period 
of restructuring

00:01:26.541 --> 00:01:29.359
